{"tid":2194212,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男學生9.6大遊行遭喬裝警拖行近20米受傷 今始獲保釋被指涉襲警","createTime":"2020-09-08T11:14:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-08T12:10:33.000Z","uid":56115,"like":7,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e471bdd789df3ae2d4f0b044248092c124d3ace7","tid":2194212,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T11:14:15.000Z","msg":"油尖旺區議會副主席余德寶稱，喬裝警拖行的楊姓學生20多歲，當日被捕後，被押往紅磡警署，四肢和背部均有損傷。他透露，警方在9月6日深夜曾通知楊同學家屬，稱可以現金500元保釋，家屬心急如焚趕至，但在警署外足足等了24小時仍未能將楊接走，「因為噚日值日官又話唔可以保釋」。<br />\n<br />\n余續指，至48小時拘留期限將滿，警方今日中午才批准楊可以保釋，但楊就因發燒在警署內送至伊利沙伯醫院，正等待武漢肺炎病毒檢測結果。楊亦被指「襲警」，下月要到警署續保。至於其餘在優才書院外被捕的幾人，他說其中一人疑涉「掟嘢」，今早獲保釋，但未知牽涉罪名；其他人的情況則未清楚。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200908/V4Y7B2ZHMZBC7HNJOTG7XJ3DVY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200908%2FV4Y7B2ZHMZBC7HNJOTG7XJ3DVY%2F&d=pZTDRaRh7CFw%2FURiZY0DNdOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=a86305e8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200908%2FV4Y7B2ZHMZBC7HNJOTG7XJ3DVY%2F&h=62f67096\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200908/V4Y7B2ZHMZBC7HNJOTG7XJ3DVY/</a>"},{"pid":"a500979c47376a9088da60c7ca428199eaccec85","tid":2194212,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T11:14:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a4dbdd0f50fe7311d544156752823496448b27c","tid":2194212,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T11:15:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d83cff8ae6a1bbe868a9ba50137a0f772e259820","tid":2194212,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T11:16:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" c